    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于这个演示</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >认识笨手笨脚的超级英雄Bob the Zhero，他意外地开始拯救自己的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在两个爆炸性的关卡中体验混乱、破坏与救援相结合的搞笑动作体验。Bob the Zhero为你带来沙盒模式中的欢乐！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于Bob the Zhero</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上与Bob一起的史诗冒险，作为他星球上最笨的超级英雄，被过分天真的居民们所包围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他们的世界需要英雄，但他们真的需要Bob吗？由你来证明！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/bb0e6c822de96fe014547bddd7b51258.poster.avif?t=1728340713\" width=518 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/bb0e6c822de96fe014547bddd7b51258.webm?t=1728340713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/bb0e6c822de96fe014547bddd7b51258.mp4?t=1728340713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>疯狂的物理效果</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助Bob通过基于物理效果的关卡，克服他世界中的日常问题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用他的吸引力将物体拉向自己，或移动到物体旁。但请小心，你的行为可能会引发意想不到的混乱！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>全面破坏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在Bob the Zhero中，几乎所有东西都是可破坏的。建筑物可以倒塌或爆炸，所有东西都可以用来制造混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在造成最小损坏的情况下，仍然成为大家所依赖的英雄吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/93e2a2919dd9306f8fd249aa307e4de1.poster.avif?t=1728340713\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/93e2a2919dd9306f8fd249aa307e4de1.webm?t=1728340713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>英雄救援</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个演示中，你需要从各种危险中拯救居民：倒塌的建筑物、爆炸、鲁莽的司机等。你很快就会发现，Bob的世界设计得并不是很好。你能成为大家期望的英雄吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/d4060f5224e77dafa0750d194cbfa1c5.poster.avif?t=1728340713\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/d4060f5224e77dafa0750d194cbfa1c5.webm?t=1728340713\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133190/extras/d4060f5224e77dafa0750d194cbfa1c5.mp4?t=1728340713\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >进入Bob the Zhero古怪的宇宙，探索一个充满惊喜和挑战的沙盒游戏。你准备好帮助Bob扮演超级英雄了吗？</p>",
